\v 20 Rumbidzai Jehovha, imwi vatumwa vake\x + Map. 148.2. Ruk. 2.13.\x*, mhare dzine simba, munoita shoko rake, kuteerera inzwi reshoko rake\x + Mat. 6.10.\x*.
\v 21 Rumbidzai Jehovha, dzihondo dzake dzese\x + Josh. 5.14. 1 Madz. 22.19.\x*\x + Map. 148.2. Ruk. 2.13.\x*, vashumiri vake\x + Map. 104.4. Dhan. 7.10.\x*, vanoita chido chake\x + Map. 40.8. 143.10. VaHeb. 1.14.\x*.
\v 22 Rumbidzai Jehovha, imwi mabasa ake ese, panzvimbo dzose dzeumambo hwake\x + Map. 145.10.\x*; rumbidza Jehovha, mweya wangu\x + 103.1,2.\x*!